  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Case control study that will include 100 participants (50 radiation exposed workers will be
        compared with 50 healthy age and sex-matched control group not exposed to radiation.

        G power program was used to calculate the sample size for two independent groups. power
        calculation estimated to detect an effect size of 0.88 of difference between means of two
        independent groups, with a p value &lt; 0.05 and 80% power,.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
